				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="Shadows of Brimstone: Challenge Pack #3 – Master of Blades" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>Of all the Lieutenants within the Fallen Shogun&amp;rsquo;s inner circle, the Takobake Blade Masters are perhaps the most terrifying. Towering mutant samurai wielding four razor sharp blades in their tentacled arms, the Blade Masters are not only expert swordsmen and strategists, but ruthless assassins, dispatched to carry out the most gruesome and sinister missions for their ambitious master.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Challenge Pack #3 &amp;ndash; Master of Blades is themed for taking on a deadly Takobake Blade Master and the army of Takobake soldiers that he commands! This set includes a new deck of Enemy Trait cards called Army of the Takobake that can be assigned to all Takobake Enemies in a Fight, giving them new and powerful abilities and behaviors. These Trait cards are used as part of the included Mission, but can also be applied to Takobake Enemies in your normal games of Shadows of Brimstone, if you want to add extra challenge to a Fight, or to theme a Mission around battling savage beastly foes!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A Challenge Pack is a new themed set of cards with a terrifying new Enemy and a nightmarish new Mission designed to give the Heroes an extra challenge. These cards are all used together for the included Mission but can also be added to your card decks to increase the challenge across your normal games of Shadows of Brimstone as well. Many of these new cards are marked with a Challenge Icon, to be easily identified as extra dangerous.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
